HEADWORD: Exaugurate
<hw>Ex*au"gu*rate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>exauguratus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>exaugurare</ets> to profane;
<ets>ex</ets> out + <ets>augurari</ets> to act as an augur, fr.
<ets>augur</ets>. ]</ety> <def>To annul the consecration of; to
secularize; to unhellow.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Holland.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
